## Technologies Used

- Programming Concept: **Advanced Object-Oriented Programming (OOPS)**
- Database Design: **ER Modeling**
- Language Used: **Java** (as per implementation)
- Tools: **DBMS concepts, UML / ER diagram design tools**

---

## Academic Purpose

This project was developed as part of **college coursework** to demonstrate:
- Strong understanding of **OOPS concepts**
- Proper **database design**
- Real-world system modeling using ER diagrams

